OL,3,CHigh Court hears Gerry Adams was
OL,4,Cbehind drive to break IRA's first
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,FA former high-ranking army
OL,8,Fintelligence officer has claimed that
OL,9,FGerry Adams was behind the push to
OL,10,Fbreak the IRA's first ceasefire with
OL,11,Fbombs in England.
OL,13,FSurvivors of the Old Bailey explosion
OL,14,Fin 1973, the London Docklands blast
OL,15,Fand Arndale shopping centre bombing in
OL,16,FManchester, both in 1996, are sueing
OL,17,Fthe former Sinn Fein President.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
