OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773853860
OL,3,CHigh Court hears Gerry Adams was
OL,4,Cbehind drive to break IRA's first
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,FThey allege the former MP was behind
OL,8,Fthe decision to bomb England and are
OL,9,Fseeking what they say is a symbolic #1
OL,10,Fin damages.
OL,12,FGerry Adams denies ever being in the
OL,13,FProvisional IRA and denies being
OL,14,Finvolved in any of these attacks.
OL,16,FOn Monday afternoon, retired Brigadier
OL,17,FIan Liles took to the stand.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
