PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773853860
OL,3,CHigh Court hears Gerry Adams was
OL,4,Cbehind drive to break IRA's first
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,FThe former commander's claims are
OL,8,Fbased on what he says he has read in
OL,9,Fintelligence reports and heard during
OL,10,Fhigh-level briefings.
OL,12,FIn his witness statement about the
OL,13,FDocklands and Manchester Bombings, the
OL,14,F71-year-old said: "I saw many
OL,15,Fintelligence intelligence reports at
OL,16,Fthe time that said Adams thought this
OL,17,Fwould be the best time to take the war
OL,18,Fto the Brits."
OL,26,@vD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
