CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773853860
OL,3,CHigh Court hears Gerry Adams was
OL,4,Cbehind drive to break IRA's first
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,F"There is no way that the bombings in
OL,8,F1996 would have happened without the
OL,9,Foversight and approval of Adams."
OL,11,FThe former intelligence officer also
OL,12,Fclaimed he saw intelligence linking
OL,13,FGerry Adams to two IRA atrocities in
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland on Bloody Friday in
OL,15,F1972 and the La Mon Bombing in 1978.
OL,17,FThe court was told despite the retired
OL,18,Fbrigadier's belief, Gerry Adams had
OL,19,Fnot been arrested over the La Mon
OL,20,Fbombing.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
