OL,3,CHigh Court hears Gerry Adams was
OL,4,Cbehind drive to break IRA's first
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,FUnder cross-examination, Brigadier
OL,8,FLiles was asked if he was a hostile
OL,9,Fwitness.
OL,11,FHe denied he had anything against the
OL,12,Fformer MP.
OL,14,F"I tried to keep peace in Northern
OL,15,FIreland. There is no motivation
OL,16,Fagainst Mr Adams. I did my job, that
OL,17,Fis it, full stop."
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
