CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773853860
OL,3,CHigh Court hears Gerry Adams was
OL,4,Cbehind drive to break IRA's first
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,FHis evidence finished when a lawyer
OL,8,Ffor Gerry Adams asked him if he was
OL,9,Faware the republican denies ever being
OL,10,Fin the IRA and any involvement in
OL,11,Fthese attacks.
OL,13,FIan Liles replied:"Of course"
OL,15,FGerry Adams, who has attended every
OL,16,Fday of this civil action, will take to
OL,17,Fthe stand in the High Court in London
OL,18,Fon Tuesday.
